            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1529156221,
            "creation_date": 1529156221,
            "body": "<p>You can generate an hash code of the entire entity.\nBasing on the hashing algorithm you choose (e.g. SHA1) the collisions are very rare.<\/p>\n",
